# Placeholder so the docs/assets/fonts/ directory ships in git even before
# the OFL Departure Mono woff2 binary lands.
#
# To vendor the font manually:
#   1. Visit https://departuremono.com/ and download the latest release zip.
#   2. Extract DepartureMono-Regular.woff2.
#   3. Place it at docs/assets/fonts/DepartureMono-Regular.woff2.
#   4. The @font-face rule in docs/css/styles.css will pick it up
#      automatically — no further changes needed.
#
# In the meantime, the JetBrains Mono Google-Fonts fallback (loaded from
# every HTML head) covers the body text so the page never falls all the
# way to system mono.
